Summary: I didn't see it, I heard it.
divs: Sighting DetailsI heard something coming down from the sky outside of my house. it had a soothing hum the sound of it. it hovered over the front of my house, I didn't look outside the front of the house because I was scared. then it flew away. It was odd, I had a bump on the side of my head under my hair, and I don't know how I got it. I can't explain both of what I just told you at all. Can you?
